Output demo/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type `./demo/run-demo.sh`
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "j"
Sleep 500ms
Type "j"
Sleep 500ms
Type "j"
Sleep 500ms

Type "/"
Sleep 500ms
Type "api"
Sleep 1500ms
Escape
Sleep 500ms

Type "t"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
Type "t"
Sleep 500ms

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
